22 March 2017, see all updates Get a unique insight into what we do at High Speed Two (HS2) Ltd and how we do it by attending one of our events. Contents Past events 
Here you can find a list of past and forthcoming events that HS2 Ltd are either hosting or attending. 
For events that took place prior to and during October and November 2014, please visit the archived events section of the HS2 website on The National Archives website 
Please note that when no future events are scheduled the ‘future events’ section will not be displayed on this page. Current and future events
